1.title: Fighting the Flood

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Officer Glen Lucas intervenes when a black bear cub gets separated from its mother and wreaks havoc on a small community. Heavy rains cause rivers to flood; Officer Eric Fluette races to rescue a man whose canoe has flipped in the rapids.

2.title: Alligator Showdown

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: Officers Bill Boudreau and Eric Hannett investigate a man raising alligators in the attic of his home. As night falls over the White Mountains, Officers Glen Lucas and Eric Fluette ascend into the darkness to rescue a lost group of hikers.

3.title: Hunter the Hunters

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: Officers Adam Cheney and Geoff Pushee run into an aggressive and angry hunter when investigating a road hunting complaint. In Whitefield, Officers Glen Lucas and Matt Holmes race to find an elderly man with dementia who's gone missing in the swamp.

4.title: Manhunt

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: Officer Glen Lucas races to the scene of an ATV accident. When a home is broken into, Officers Bill Boudreau and Eric Hannett assist police in tracking the suspect. Meanwhile, Officer Bob Mancini tries to save the life of an injured loon.

5.title: No Way Out

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: When the circumstances of a deer kill seem unlikely, Officers Bob Mancini and Kevin Bronson investigate the hunter's claim. Then, Conservation Officers work with rescue volunteers to recover the body of a missing hiker on Mt. Washington.

6.title: Into Thin Air

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Officer Glen Lucas makes a dangerous trek to the summit of Mt. Washington to rescue a stranded and injured hiker. Then, Officers Eric Hannett and Bill Boudreau track down a trio of possible deer poachers.

7.title: When Duty Calls

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: Officers Murphy and Demler investigate a suspicious turkey kill while Officer Courtney rescues a scared fawn near a busy intersection. Officer Lucas races to save a sick loon and Officer Flute helps a hiker find his father who is lost in the woods.

8.title: On the Run

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: In New Hampshire, Officer Hannett pursues an unusual recreational vehicle in a high speed chase. Officer Pushee and Trainee Discoll encounter a group of combative speedsters. And Officer Lucas races to the scene of an ATV crash.

9.title: Truth or Consequences

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: In New Hampshire, Officer Glen Lucas investigates a dispute between a turkey hunter and an eyewitness. Sergeant Todd Szewczyk hunts down a trespassing target shooter and Officers McKee and Matson fish for the truth from trespassing ATV riders.

10.title: Blindsided

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: Officer Hannett is tested trying to capture an injured goose. Officer Lucas is the first responder on scene for a drug overdose. And Officer MacFadzen must climb 40 feet into the treetops to deal with an aggressive hawk.

11.title: Under Suspicion

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: Officers Hannett and Boudreau interrogate a group about lighting a fire in the woods. Officers Cheney and McKee confront a sly fisherman with a habit of lying. And officers discover a lobster man who is banned from state waters breaking the law.

12.title: Crossing the Line

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: Officer Kevin Bronson races to get a driver under the influence off the road. Officer Eric Hannett catches two teenagers joyriding on a public road. And up north, Officer Mancini helps evacuate an injured hiker.

8.title: On the Run

episode of.title: North Woods Law: New Hampshire (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: In New Hampshire, Officer Hannett pursues an unusual recreational vehicle in a high speed chase. Officer Pushee and Trainee Driscoll encounter a group of combative speedsters. And Officer Lucas races to the scene of an ATV crash.
